\par\plain {\f1\fs22\b0\i1\cf4 [ Let's start off the scene with a setting description, to set the scene up. This is the first time that the readers will be inside Evan's guest bedroom. Here are some things to include in your description.<!$Scr_Ps::0><$Scr_Ps::1>}
\par\pard\plain \tx235\tx720\li720\fi14\sl262\slmult1\ltrch\loch \ls1\ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 Queen-size bed.}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 Very clean and well kept.}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 Private guest bathroom, that is fully stocked, with hairdryer, soap, towels, toothbrushes \endash  essentially anything a guess would need for an unexpected stay.}
\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf5 Guest bathroom is also very clean.<!$Scr_Ps::1><$Scr_Ps::0>}
